          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1-1651056565825-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>soy sauce </strong>to a plate then dip the <strong>tofu slices</strong> into the <strong>soy sauce</strong> and add them to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray, pouring any <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong> over the top</p><p>Top the tofu slices with the <strong>smoked sea salt flakes</strong> and 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> generous grinds of <strong>black pepper</strong>,<strong> </strong>then put the tray in the oven for an initial 7-8 min</p><p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>in half</p><p>Peel and grate the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1651056573136-x200.jpg",
