    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a small pot over a medium heat and add the juice of the <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with 25ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[35ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong>, the <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong>,<strong> ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce has thickened to a syrup-like consistency, then remove it from the heat and set aside – this is your<strong> BBQ sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
