    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 7-8 min, remove the tofu from the oven and add a spoonful of the <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> to each slice (you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 10-12 min or until warmed through and sticky – this is your <strong>Texas-style dalmatian tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
