    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>shredded red cabbage </strong>to the reserved bowl with the <strong>mayo </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span>of the <strong>pickling liquid </strong>from the quick-pickled cucumber</p><p>Season with a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix everything together – this is your <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
